,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>慢喎 你試吓換個條lan線</blockquote><br />\n已經換哂做cat6 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無線加密用左tkip？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff397d65dc5247f14f001d111e2375344eeaead3","tid":158383,"uid":74943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"搭單一問，用緊網上行30mbs上網，router直插電腦上網， speedtest正常但一打機就狂跳ping...有咩原因會導致咁?"},{"pid":"13e7d22b1fba7504221854db2d4ddd0a8a6bb6e1","tid":158383,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單一問，用緊網上行30mbs上網，router直插電腦上網， speedtest正常但一打機就狂跳ping...有咩原因會導致咁?</blockquote><br />\n確保隻router冇其他人用緊，而且唔好download野，唔好睇片，正常應該唔會跳得好勁。"},{"pid":"2bbf647356572451ec8af1427d0ac98197299599","tid":158383,"uid":74943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單一問，用緊網上行30mbs上網，router直插電腦上網， speedtest正常但一打機就狂跳ping...有咩原因會導致咁?</blockquote><br />\n確保隻router冇其他人用緊，而且唔好download野，唔好睇片，正常應該唔會跳得好勁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係全屋企得我一個用，冇upload/download野都會有咁既情況...好灰，網上行又話唔關佢地事"},{"pid":"b70baccdb35055090db24b9f5cc852a6afa1c392","tid":158383,"uid":83698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>慢喎 你試吓換個條lan線</blockquote><br />\n已經換哂做cat6 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無線加密用左tkip？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60432bbc28c9809def592e46d95d6f4c3416221","tid":158383,"uid":83698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你用咩adapter？<br />\n單天線433<br />\n雙天線866<br />\n三天線1300</b